        public static java.lang.String getVerovio(java.lang.Object caller)
        This method retreives the latest online Verovio Toolkit JavaScript script. If not available, it returns the local version that ships with meico.
        Parameters:
        caller -
        Returns:
        the Verovio Toolkit JavaScript script or null if even the local version cannot be read
